  "detailed_description": "<h1>Предыстория истории</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Chushpan Simulator 2 is a story-driven adventure with RPG elements. The events of the game unfold after the finale of the first part. Egor and Nastya were traveling along a road that served as neutral territory, dividing the domains of two rival gangs - the Asphalt Pavers and the Glassblowers. They hoped that the recent truce between these groups would ensure their safe passage. But suddenly, the Asphalt Pavers ambushed them. Nastya was kidnapped, and Egor was left alone in hostile territory.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In the game, you will:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Explore the Old City</strong></li></ul>Unlock new locations, find valuable items, and gather useful information.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024830/extras/3475156d64d3cc225c31834e885bbf4c.poster.avif?t=1769867015\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024830/extras/3475156d64d3cc225c31834e885bbf4c.webm?t=1769867015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024830/extras/3475156d64d3cc225c31834e885bbf4c.mp4?t=1769867015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Complete a variety of missions</strong></li></ul>By completing quests for the gangs, you choose between friendly or hostile relations with different groups, affecting the storyline and events.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024830/extras/e2a462f7aea02e8289bc961b6da4ee69.poster.avif?t=1769867015\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024830/extras/e2a462f7aea02e8289bc961b6da4ee69.webm?t=1769867015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024830/extras/e2a462f7aea02e8289bc961b6da4ee69.mp4?t=1769867015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Develop Combat Skills</strong></li></ul>Use firearms and improve your melee skills, employing various tactics and weapons.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024830/extras/92e313a8307ab9454f524445d6253b4b.poster.avif?t=1769867015\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024830/extras/92e313a8307ab9454f524445d6253b4b.webm?t=1769867015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024830/extras/92e313a8307ab9454f524445d6253b4b.mp4?t=1769867015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Study Zombie Behavior</strong></li></ul>Find effective ways to combat zombies by studying their habits and weaknesses.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024830/extras/7ccecd15a9dfc1429762696d6f62a426.poster.avif?t=1769867015\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024830/extras/7ccecd15a9dfc1429762696d6f62a426.webm?t=1769867015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024830/extras/7ccecd15a9dfc1429762696d6f62a426.mp4?t=1769867015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Hacking and Exploration</strong></li></ul>Apply hacking skills and find keys to open locked doors and containers, uncovering hidden treasures and resources.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024830/extras/624383c0ae9b8fd1e3e3b6e1d45a883d.poster.avif?t=1769867015\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024830/extras/624383c0ae9b8fd1e3e3b6e1d45a883d.webm?t=1769867015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024830/extras/624383c0ae9b8fd1e3e3b6e1d45a883d.mp4?t=1769867015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Immerse yourself in a dangerous world where every decision matters, and help Egor rescue Nastya, overcoming all obstacles on the path to a happy future.",
